    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >关于这款游戏</h2>《克加菜》是一款融合了冒险，烹饪与收集要素的游戏，你将扮演冒险家在冰天雪地中捕猎怪物，制作美食，开办深渊食堂。与食客们交朋友会帮助你获得神谕，从而得到各种特殊的能力。<br>除了常见的人类美食，这片大陆的怪物提供了更丰富的食材清单，你将制作一些与众不同的黑暗料理，并因此结识来自深渊的食客。无论是美食还是神谕，都将帮助你在这片远离人类的大陆上走得更远，走得更“深”……<br>是的，深渊在凝视你。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >深渊食堂</h2>在篝火边的夜晚，来自深渊的生物会前来拜访。<br>用捕猎的怪物做成美味菜肴招待它们吧！你将得到黑暗的馈赠。<br>随着菜谱的扩充和烹饪技术的提升，还会触发特殊剧情。<br>隐藏在迷雾中的怪物历史，将由它们一一讲述。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187680/extras/3fe8bfc37d27e77532aab1b40222fedb.poster.avif?t=1730188836\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187680/extras/3fe8bfc37d27e77532aab1b40222fedb.webm?t=1730188836\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187680/extras/3fe8bfc37d27e77532aab1b40222fedb.mp4?t=1730188836\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >野外探险</h2>从浮冰岛屿开始，探索这片蛮荒的冰雪大陆。<br>各种变异怪物和神话生物将给你的冒险增加趣（难）味（度）性。<br>篝火会在夜晚守护你的安全，而灯塔会帮助你发现新的陆地，拓展你的旅程。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187680/extras/0abd770f5a5470ec752073c4351bbcd9.poster.avif?t=1730188836\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187680/extras/0abd770f5a5470ec752073c4351bbcd9.webm?t=1730188836\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187680/extras/0abd770f5a5470ec752073c4351bbcd9.mp4?t=1730188836\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >神谕之虫</h2>深渊食堂和探险收获，都可能产出神谕虫。<br>它们会在你的大脑中组成图形，带来古神的祝福。<br>要小心这些神谕，带来特殊效果的同时，也会让你支付代价。<br>尤其注意对理智的影响。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187680/extras/d4d6081dc91a9e4d1438f10ae392d788.poster.avif?t=1730188836\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187680/extras/d4d6081dc91a9e4d1438f10ae392d788.webm?t=1730188836\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187680/extras/d4d6081dc91a9e4d1438f10ae392d788.mp4?t=1730188836\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2>特性丰富的QTE战斗<br>装备打造与背包管理<br>各式各样的怪物，并有概率遇到变异怪物娘<br>自由组合的神谕之虫，赋予不同超凡能力<br>多个剧情角色，个人剧情等待探索<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >生存指南</h2>危险无处不在，越漂亮的越危险！<br>保持理智，建议苟在篝火过夜。<br>小心大胃客人，宁可少赚一点，也别把自己倒贴出去。",
